      "rdf:value": "<L>121031<pc>613,3<k1>pAkayajYa<k2>pAka—yajYa<e>3\r\n<s>pAka—yajYa</s> ¦ &c. See under <hom>2.</hom> <s>pAka</s>.<info hui=\"a\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3ApAkayajYa#record-pwg",
      "@type": "csl:SourceRecord",
      "dct:source": "Boehtlingk-Roth PWG",
      "csl:dictionary": "pwg",
      "csl:recordNumber": "43966",
      "csl:lineNumber": 430459,
      "csl:pageColumn": "4-0623",
      "rdf:value": "<L>43966<pc>4-0623<k1>pAkayajYa<k2>pAkayajYa/\n{#pAkayajYa/#}¦ (1. {#pAka + yajYa#}) <lex>m.</lex>\n<div n=\"1\"> 1) {%ein schlichtes, einfaches Opfer, häusliches Opfer%}; so heissen nach\n<ls>ĀPASTAMBA</ls> : <is>Aupāsanahoma</is>, <is>Vaiśvadeva</is>, <is>Pārvaṇa</is>, <is>Aṣṭakā</is>, <is>Śrāddha</is>, <is>Sarpabali</is>, <is>Īśānabali</is>; nach BAUDHĀJANA: <is>Huta</is>, <is>Prahuta</is>, <is>Āhuta</is>, <is>Śūlagava</is>, <is>Baliharaṇa</is>, <is>Pratyavarohaṇa</is>, <is>Aṣṭakāhoma</is>, <ab>Comm.</ab> zu <ls>TS. 1,7,1,1</ls>\n; nach <ls>GAUTAMA</ls> : <is>Aṣṭakā</is>, <is>Pārvaṇa</is>, <is>Śrāddha</is>, <is>Śrāvaṇī</is>, <is>Āgrahāyaṇī</is>, <is>Caitrī</is>, <is>Āśvayujī</is>,\n<ab>Schol.</ab> zu <ls>KĀTY. ŚR. 34,8.</ls> <ls>M. MÜLLER</ls> in <ls>Z. d. d. m. G. IX, LXXIII.</ls> Eine Dreitheilung giebt\n<ls>ĀŚV. GṚHY. 1,1</ls> : {#trayaH pAkayajYA hutA agnO hUyamAnA anagnO prahutA brAhmaRaBojane brahmaRi hutAH#}; vier Arten nach\n<ls>M. 2,86</ls> ({#vESvadevahomabalikarmanityaSrAdDAtiTiBojanAtmakAH#}\n<ls>KULL.</ls>). {#pAkayajYAnsamAsAdyEkAjyAnekabarhizaH . ekasvizwakftaH kuryAnnAnApi sati dEvate#}\n<ls>ĀŚV. GṚHY. 1,3. 10.</ls>\n<ls>TS. 1,7,1,1.</ls> <ls n=\"TS.\">6,2,5,3.</ls>\n<ls>AIT. BR. 3,40.</ls> {#pAkayajYA ityAcakzata ekAgnO yajYAn#}\n<ls>LĀṬY. 4,9,2.</ls> <ls>KAUŚ. 6. 45.</ls> <ls>ŚAT. BR. 1,4,2,10.</ls> <ls n=\"ŚAT. BR. 1,\">8,1,7.</ls> <ls n=\"ŚAT. BR.\">2,3,1,21.</ls> <ls>KĀTY. ŚR. 6,10,29.</ls> <ls>PĀR.</ls> <ls>GṚHY. 1,4. 3,12.</ls> <ls>ŚĀṄKH. GṚHY. 1,1. 10.</ls> <ls>M. 2,143.</ls> <ls n=\"M.\">11,118.</ls> <ls>MBH. 3,1132.</ls> <ls n=\"MBH. 3,\">14147.</ls> <ls n=\"MBH.\">12,2437.</ls> <ls>VP. 292.</ls> <ls>BHĀG. P. 6,19,21.</ls> <ls>BHAVIṢYA-P.</ls> in <ls>Verz. d. Oxf. H. 30,b,6.</ls> <ab>Vgl.</ab> <ls>M.</ls> <ls>MÜLLER, SL. 203.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) <ab>N. pr.</ab> eines Mannes: {#iti ha smAha pAkayajYa EqaH#}\n<ls>GOBH. 1,9,16.</ls>\n<LEND>"
    },
